<lb n="0667a08"/><head type="no">No. 1881</head>
<lb n="0667a09"/><div1 type="xu"><mulu type="序" level="1" label="金師子章序"/><head><note n="0667001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】宋紹聖三年刊宮內省圖書寮藏本，【甲】大日本續藏經，校者曰此序者依甲本載之</note>金師子章序</head>
<lb n="0667a10"/>
<lb n="0667a11"/><p>夫龍象之蹴踏於乾坤。開奧藏兮說妙法。蟣
<lb n="0667a12"/>蟻之趹&CB05113;於土塊。傳深法兮轉法輪。杜順智
<lb n="0667a13"/>儼祖師既滂大法於碧落。香象清涼賢德早
<lb n="0667a14"/>話明&CB05058;於黃泉<note place="inline">矣</note>。所以雖大聖之說傳一味。
<lb n="0667a15"/>華嚴一乘秀眾教。雖弘經之達士其德同。香
<lb n="0667a16"/>象獨勝餘師焉。爰於如來出興之法。有何教
<lb n="0667a17"/>教內而不見其說否。設有教內而不見其說。
<lb n="0667a18"/>有教外而有其文否。設有教外而有其文。說
<lb n="0667a19"/>權之五十一品之名。而不隔歷其位否。設有
<lb n="0667a20"/>說其位之名不隔歷。於十信之初位。盡五十
<lb n="0667a21"/>二品之功。證得無生忍。斷盡無明者否。復有
<lb n="0667a22"/>甚教說一於。而包三世間之說否。設不對權
<lb n="0667a23"/>教故。名之曰別教。是非隔別之故云別。不廢
<lb n="0667a24"/>權立實之教。頓實者否。設有頓實者。其經說
<lb n="0667a25"/>處純淨土而莊嚴微妙否。設有其處淨土而
<lb n="0667a26"/>莊嚴微妙。非變化而真土否。設有非變化而
<lb n="0667a27"/>真土。於所說之法不約理。而以事顯性者否。
<lb n="0667a28"/>復有那經於序首直烈深位之菩薩否。復有那
<lb n="0667a29"/>教首隔二乘。顯身土之高廣。終攝二乘。密顯
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0667b" n="0667b"/>
<lb n="0667b01"/>三世間一而不缺之義否。設有攝二乘。直有益
<lb n="0667b02"/>女人否。設有利撫女人。有現坐之得益五百
<lb n="0667b03"/>否。設有那經不離自國兮得果否。設有不離
<lb n="0667b04"/>自國兮悟道者。現以龍畜身兮悟道者否。設
<lb n="0667b05"/>以龍畜身兮悟道者。其數一萬否。設有少分。
<lb n="0667b06"/>以龍畜之身悟道者。不言攝闡提否<note place="inline">闡提者。是三世間。又
<lb n="0667b07"/>中眾生世間也</note>設有攝闡提。備說中道否。設有說中
<lb n="0667b08"/>道。正有說止觀否。設有說止觀之名。現說十
<lb n="0667b09"/>如否。設有說十如。正有後方便者否。設有方
<lb n="0667b10"/>便。切有不依橫計與空花二妄否。設有不墮
<lb n="0667b11"/>二妄。有譬高山先得蒙性光之照益否。設少
<lb n="0667b12"/>分有是益。於教主之故光因果俱時否。設有
<lb n="0667b13"/>因果俱時。非暫時之益否。設有非暫時之益。
<lb n="0667b14"/>於其佛現實報。而有包十身通三世間否。設
<lb n="0667b15"/>有其文。復有具十頭十眼十耳十鼻十口十
<lb n="0667b16"/>舌十身十手十足十智十如十忍十明十通十
<lb n="0667b17"/>解脫十辨十音十無畏十不具法十佛土十處
<lb n="0667b18"/>十會十菩薩十波羅蜜十方便十願。如是十
<lb n="0667b19"/>十無盡事事無礙事事理理圓融之法否。唯
<lb n="0667b20"/>此一經具此諸德<note place="inline">矣</note>。所以談之教內。世尊拍
<lb n="0667b21"/>膝。傳之祖道。三佛卷舌。提祖之就變札於鴈
<lb n="0667b22"/>足。&CB00444;胡國於楊州。韻保之梳粉髮於南風。催
<lb n="0667b23"/>舊淚於&CB00470;林。此皆國土世間之說法。如來&M010527;
<lb n="0667b24"/>說之華嚴也。以佛賀出&CB01894;於口中。切普賢億
<lb n="0667b25"/>億之頂。祖室&CB01769;手於法箭。破毘盧純一之貌。
<lb n="0667b26"/>既往獨說之家無利益。流派之境有功德。師
<lb n="0667b27"/>子之齘破一塵兮出大經卷。大象之&CB05067;迷大
<lb n="0667b28"/>虛收粟中<note place="inline">矣</note>。復有那師文義共遍通達一代
<lb n="0667b29"/>所說之經法否。設有通達一代。立五教。判聖
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0667c" n="0667c"/>
<lb n="0667c01"/>教。超先代否。設有判教超他德。說道超世。教
<lb n="0667c02"/>化同佛否。設有說道超他。入經藏對三藏勝
<lb n="0667c03"/>論議人否。設有對三藏論議人。有傳教教人
<lb n="0667c04"/>得教外益否。設有令得教外益。從口現出五
<lb n="0667c05"/>光人否。設有出光人。所出光變成寶蓋否。設
<lb n="0667c06"/>有光成寶蓋。舉世號小釋迦否。設有號小釋
<lb n="0667c07"/>迦。入王宮為御見拜否。設有為王被拜。為皇
<lb n="0667c08"/>后見拜。并為皇后說經典否。設有為皇后被
<lb n="0667c09"/>拜。及立寺塔被歸依。現身不易生。昇都率否。
<lb n="0667c10"/>設有登都率。門徒繁昌六國。所流之法不斷
<lb n="0667c11"/>絕。于今盛否<note place="inline">矣</note>。爰金師子章者。依則天皇后
<lb n="0667c12"/>請。藏大師之所說也。文約而義深。言少而意
<lb n="0667c13"/>廣。是則破小塵兮出大經卷。約大虛兮置一
<lb n="0667c14"/>毛中。大悟指掌。現益扶手。碩學大悟之菩薩
<lb n="0667c15"/>阿不勤行者乎。若欲繼佛祖之跡。欲傳事事
<lb n="0667c16"/>無礙之功者。先須結跏趺坐。或用半跏趺坐。
<lb n="0667c17"/>謂正大座之時。一卜坐處於閑寂。上用蒲團。
<lb n="0667c18"/>略明方軌。雖不事一順。向面於初地方。當後
<lb n="0667c19"/>於十向處。以左足在右&CB00170;上。舉右足安左&CB00170;
<lb n="0667c20"/>上。以右手安右&CB00170;上。舉左手在右掌中。教二
<lb n="0667c21"/>之大拇指面與面相柱<note place="inline">矣</note>。凡正坐之時。不得
<lb n="0667c22"/>右側左傾前低後仰。須耳與肩對鼻與臍相
<lb n="0667c23"/>向。以舌拄上&CB00171;。唇與唇。上齒與下齒相近。眼
<lb n="0667c24"/>似開不開。似閉不閉。是學大聖之人方軌也
<lb n="0667c25"/>焉。次半跏趺坐者。舉左足壓右&CB00170;若也。須以
<lb n="0667c26"/>止觀之行可依無念一門。念發則隨發。不發
<lb n="0667c27"/>念者是有念也。生死何休。發念隨念則無念
<lb n="0667c28"/>也。是名大涅槃。無念之無念。無相之無相。有
<lb n="0667c29"/>念之有念。有相之有相。皆悉外道之所執也。
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0668a" n="0668a"/>
<lb n="0668a01"/>更非佛家之說法也。請願諸有心倫。蹄釋迦
<lb n="0668a02"/>佛之海印三昧藏大師之事事觀門。莫依小
<lb n="0668a03"/>乘家之滅盡三昧外道宗之惡邪執<note place="inline">矣耳</note></p>
<lb n="0668a04"/>
<lb n="0668a05"/>
<lb n="0668a06"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead><note n="0668001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大方廣佛華嚴經金師子章＝註金師子章一卷【甲】</note><app n="0668001"><lem>大方廣佛華嚴經金師子章</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">註金師子章一卷</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0668a07"/>
<lb n="0668a08"/><byline type="Author"><note n="0668002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此前甲本有唐崇福寺沙門法藏述九字</note>五臺山真容院沙門承遷註</byline>
<lb n="0668a09"/><p><note n="0668003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（華嚴經）＋金【甲】</note><app n="0668003"><lem>金</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">華嚴經金</rdg></app>師子章　金師子者。能喻<note n="0668004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔法〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668004"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>也。究其本
<lb n="0668a10"/><note n="0668005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔元〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668005"><lem>元</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>即<note n="0668006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝巨【甲】</note><app n="0668006"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">巨</rdg></app>。唐賢首法師對<note n="0668007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則天聖帝＝天帝【甲】</note><app n="0668007"><lem>則天聖帝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">天帝</rdg></app>。<note n="0668008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以示大經厥＝示華嚴經【甲】</note><app n="0668008"><lem>以示
<lb n="0668a11"/>大經厥</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">示華嚴經</rdg></app>旨。所謂<note n="0668009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">華嚴＝大經【甲】</note><app n="0668009"><lem>華嚴</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大經</rdg></app>理深事廣文博義玄。非
<lb n="0668a12"/>入理聖人無以達其奧。是以立見邊之喻。曉
<lb n="0668a13"/>無涯之法。金況法界體也。師子喻法界用也。
<lb n="0668a14"/><note n="0668010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今則…得）十四字∞（理事…矣）九字【甲】</note><note n="0668010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（今則從法就喻略啟十門分別故得）十四字∞（理事鎔融一多無礙矣）九字【甲】</note><app n="0668010"><lem>今則從法就喻。略啟十門分別<note n="0668011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故得＝一明緣起【甲】</note><app n="0668011"><lem>故。得</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一明緣起</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">理事鎔融一多無礙矣</rdg></app><note n="0668012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今則…得）十四字∞（理事…矣）九字【甲】</note><note n="0668012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（今則從法就喻略啟十門分別故得）十四字∞（理事鎔融一多無礙矣）九字【甲】</note><app n="0668012"><lem>理事
<lb n="0668a15"/>鎔融一多無<note n="0668013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">礙矣＝閡【甲】</note><app n="0668013"><lem>礙矣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">閡</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">今則從法就喻略啟十門分別故得</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668a16"/><byline type="Other"><note n="0668014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔唐崇…述〕十一字－【甲】</note><app n="0668014" word-count="11"><lem>唐崇福寺賢首法師法藏述</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0668a17"/><p><note n="0668015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔初明緣起〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668015"><lem>初明緣起</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>　<note n="0668016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">萬＝物【甲】</note><app n="0668016"><lem>萬</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">物</rdg></app>像本空。假緣方有</p>
<lb n="0668a18"/><p>二辨色空　幻法紛然。真空不動</p>
<lb n="0668a19"/><p>三約三性　迷之名相。悟之即真</p>
<lb n="0668a20"/><p>四顯無相　相即無相。非相即相</p>
<lb n="0668a21"/><p>五說無生　無生之生。生即無生</p>
<lb n="0668a22"/><p>六論五教　根器不同。<note n="0668017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">設＝立【甲】</note><app n="0668017"><lem>設</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">立</rdg></app>教有異</p>
<lb n="0668a23"/><p>七<note n="0668018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勒＝勤【甲】</note><app n="0668018"><lem>勒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">勤</rdg></app>十玄　緣起交映。法法<note n="0668019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">重重＝無盡【甲】</note><app n="0668019"><lem>重重</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">無盡</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668a24"/><p>八括六相　法無定相。舉一即多</p>
<lb n="0668a25"/><p>九成菩提　萬行既圓。本覺<note n="0668020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">露＝顯【甲】</note><app n="0668020"><lem>露</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">顯</rdg></app>現</p>
<lb n="0668a26"/><p>十入涅槃　智體<note n="0668021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＝如【甲】</note><app n="0668021"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>如。名大涅<note n="0668022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">槃＋（大緣起萬有有必顯於多門無性一宗宗蓋彰於眾德分其體用卷舒之趣易明覽其玄網理事之門方曉今就所喻之法略明緣起之理也）五十四字【甲】</note><app n="0668022"><lem>槃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">槃大緣起萬有有必顯於多門無性一宗宗蓋彰於眾德分其體用卷舒之趣易明覽其玄網理事之門方曉今就所喻之法略明緣起之理也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668a27"/><p><note n="0668023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔第〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0668023"><lem>第</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一明緣起者　謂萬法無體。假緣成立。若
<lb n="0668a28"/>無因緣。法即不生。故經云。諸法從緣<note n="0668024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">起＝生【甲】＊</note><app n="0668024"><lem>起</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>。無
<lb n="0668a29"/>緣即不<anchor id="fxT45p0668a01"/>起</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0668b" n="0668b"/>
<lb n="0668b01"/><p>謂<note n="0668025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0668025"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>金無自性　<note n="0668026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔喻〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0668026"><lem>喻</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>真理不變<note n="0668027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0668027"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668b02"/><p>隨<note n="0668028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（工）＋巧【甲】</note><app n="0668028"><lem>巧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">工巧</rdg></app>匠之緣遂有師<note n="0668029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="0668029"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">子之</rdg></app>相起　<anchor id="fxT45p0668b01"/>喻真<note n="0668030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">理＝如【甲】</note><app n="0668030"><lem>理</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>隨
<lb n="0668b03"/>緣成諸事法<anchor id="fxT45p0668b02"/>也</p>
<lb n="0668b04"/><p>起但是緣故名緣起　<note n="0668031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔結〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668031"><lem>結</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>真理不動動<note n="0668032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668032"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>事
<lb n="0668b05"/>也。金喻一真之<note n="0668033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（理）＋性【甲】</note><app n="0668033"><lem>性</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">理性</rdg></app>。師子喻緣起事法。理本
<lb n="0668b06"/>無生。隨諸緣法成差別相。<note n="0668034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔相〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668034"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>起繁興理即無
<lb n="0668b07"/>生。<note n="0668035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0668035"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>清涼云。理隨事變。則一多緣起之無
<lb n="0668b08"/><note n="0668036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">邊＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0668036"><lem>邊</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">邊也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668b09"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0668b03"/>第二辨色空者　色者悲也。空者智也。觀色
<lb n="0668b10"/>即空成大智。而不住生死。觀空即色成大悲。
<lb n="0668b11"/>而不滯涅槃。能<note n="0668037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辯之智＝辨教【甲】</note><app n="0668037"><lem>辯之智</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">辨教</rdg></app>煥然明<note n="0668038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">了＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0668038"><lem>了</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">了也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668b12"/><p>謂<anchor id="fxT45p0668b04"/>以師子相虛　<anchor id="fxT45p0668b05"/>喻色<note n="0668039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空＋（是）【甲】</note><app n="0668039"><lem>空</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">空是</rdg></app>也</p>
<lb n="0668b13"/><p>唯是真金　<anchor id="fxT45p0668b06"/>喻性實<anchor id="fxT45p0668b07"/>也</p>
<lb n="0668b14"/><p>師子不有　<anchor id="fxT45p0668b08"/>喻<note n="0668040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">緣起＝從緣【甲】</note><app n="0668040"><lem>緣起</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">從緣</rdg></app>幻色不是實有</p>
<lb n="0668b15"/><p>金體不無　<anchor id="fxT45p0668b09"/>喻<note n="0668041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">真＝實【甲】</note><app n="0668041"><lem>真</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">實</rdg></app>空常存</p>
<lb n="0668b16"/><p>故云色空。又復空無自性。約色以明不<note n="0668042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">礙幻存故名＝閡幻有名為【甲】</note><app n="0668042"><lem>礙幻
<lb n="0668b17"/>存故名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">閡幻有名為</rdg></app>色空　<note n="0668043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（謂）＋真【甲】</note><app n="0668043"><lem>真</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">謂真</rdg></app>空無形。假色相以<note n="0668044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="0668044"><lem>明</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">明之</rdg></app>。法
<lb n="0668b18"/>本<note n="0668045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亡＝云【甲】</note><app n="0668045"><lem>亡</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">云</rdg></app>言。就言詮而顯道。<anchor id="fxT45p0668b10"/>故清涼云。雖空
<lb n="0668b19"/><note n="0668046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔空〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668046"><lem>空</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>絕&CB00528;。而義<note n="0668047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="0668047"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">天之</rdg></app>星<note n="0668048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">像＝象【甲】＊</note><app n="0668048"><lem>像</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">象</rdg></app>璨<note n="0668049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">然＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0668049"><lem>然</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">然也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668b20"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0668b11"/>第三約三性者　迷心所執計有相生以為
<lb n="0668b21"/>實者。謂之偏計性也。不了緣生依他性也。
<lb n="0668b22"/><note n="0668050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔依他〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668050"><lem>依他</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無性即是圓<note n="0668051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成＋（性也）【甲】</note><app n="0668051"><lem>成</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">成性也</rdg></app>。隨舉一法三性具矣</p>
<lb n="0668b23"/><p>謂<anchor id="fxT45p0668b12"/>以師子情有名為<note n="0668052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遍＝偏【甲】＊</note><app n="0668052"><lem>遍</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">偏</rdg></app>計　謂一切眾生無
<lb n="0668b24"/>始已來煩惱業習癡迷不了。周<anchor id="fxT45p0668b13"/>遍計度心外
<lb n="0668b25"/>有法。顛倒取捨。隨情起惑。自纏自縛。<note n="0668053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枉＝拙【甲】</note><app n="0668053"><lem>枉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">拙</rdg></app>受
<lb n="0668b26"/>輪迴</p>
<lb n="0668b27"/><p>師子似有名為依他　謂一切眾生依真起
<lb n="0668b28"/><note n="0668054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妄＋（現）【甲】</note><app n="0668054"><lem>妄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">妄現</rdg></app>。似有之法妄執依他內外不實。故論云。
<lb n="0668b29"/>依他起自性分別緣所<note n="0668055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0668055"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">生也</rdg></app></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0668c" n="0668c"/>
<lb n="0668c01"/><p>金性不變故<note n="0668056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">號＝名【甲】</note><app n="0668056"><lem>號</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">名</rdg></app>圓成　圓而不減。成而不增。
<lb n="0668c02"/>師子雖則相殊。金且不<note n="0668057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隨殊變釋曰法＝壞謂【甲】</note><app n="0668057"><lem>隨殊變。釋曰。法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">壞謂</rdg></app>與
<lb n="0668c03"/>自心為緣。心法方起。今了緣無體。依心方現。
<lb n="0668c04"/>無自體<note n="0668058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">性＝生【甲】</note><app n="0668058"><lem>性</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>。是為依他無<note n="0668059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔自〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668059"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>生性。由二義現
<lb n="0668c05"/>前。乃為圓成勝義<note n="0668060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">性也＝生【甲】</note><app n="0668060"><lem>性也</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>。經云。從無住本立
<lb n="0668c06"/>一切<note n="0668061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0668061"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">法也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668c07"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0668c01"/>第四顯無相者　不了<note n="0668062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸法而〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668062"><lem>諸法而</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無相迷<note n="0668063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝之【甲】</note><app n="0668063"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>
<lb n="0668c08"/>為有<note n="0668064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【甲】</note><app n="0668064"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>生死也。觀察即虛相即無相出世法
<lb n="0668c09"/>也</p>
<lb n="0668c10"/><p>謂以金收師子盡　喻理奪<note n="0668065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">事＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0668065"><lem>事</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">事也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668c11"/><p>金外更無師<note n="0668066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（相）【甲】</note><app n="0668066"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">子相</rdg></app>可得　<anchor id="fxT45p0668c02"/>喻緣起事法當體本
<lb n="0668c12"/><note n="0668067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虛＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0668067"><lem>虛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">虛也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668c13"/><p>故名無相　<note n="0668068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">釋曰離真理＝謂真【甲】</note><app n="0668068"><lem>釋曰。離真理</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">謂真</rdg></app>外無片事可得故。
<lb n="0668c14"/>如水奪波波無不盡故。此則水存以壞波令
<lb n="0668c15"/><note n="0668069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0668069"><lem>盡</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">盡也</rdg></app>。故經云。所見不可見。所聞不可聞。了知
<lb n="0668c16"/>諸世間。是名為無相</p>
<lb n="0668c17"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0668c03"/>第五說無生者　法本無生。從緣有故。既無
<lb n="0668c18"/>自體。生而無<note n="0668070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0668070"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">生也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0668c19"/><p>謂<anchor id="fxT45p0668c04"/>以正見師子生時但是金生　<anchor id="fxT45p0668c05"/>喻真理隨
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0669a" n="0669a"/>
<lb n="0669a01"/>緣成諸事法</p>
<lb n="0669a02"/><p>金外更無一物　離真理之外無別事相。染
<lb n="0669a03"/>淨之法因緣有。故體性本虛無<note n="0669001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="0669001"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">生之</rdg></app>生也</p>
<lb n="0669a04"/><p>師子雖有生滅金體本無增減　無生之理本
<lb n="0669a05"/>無生滅。緣起集成生本無生</p>
<lb n="0669a06"/><p>故曰無生　<note n="0669002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">釋曰今＝謂金【甲】</note><app n="0669002"><lem>釋曰。今</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">謂金</rdg></app>由緣生。非生方得名
<lb n="0669a07"/><note n="0669003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔生〕－【甲】</note><app n="0669003"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。了<note n="0669004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生死性＝無【甲】</note><app n="0669004"><lem>生死性</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>乃是無生。論云。因不自生。緣
<lb n="0669a08"/>生故。緣不自生。因生故。然生與無生互成互
<lb n="0669a09"/>奪。奪則無生。成乃緣生。由即成即奪。是故生
<lb n="0669a10"/>時無生。如是了者<note n="0669005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名達＝故名【甲】</note><app n="0669005"><lem>名達</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">故名</rdg></app>無生</p>
<lb n="0669a11"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669a01"/>第六論五教<note n="0669006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（一聲…第一））二十六字＝（（者一愚法））四字【甲】</note><app n="0669006" word-count="26"><lem>一聲聞教二大乘始教三大乘
<lb n="0669a12"/>終教四大乘頓教五一乘圖教第一</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">者一愚法</rdg></app>聲聞教謂
<lb n="0669a13"/>此師子雖是<note n="0669007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">緣生＝因緣【甲】</note><app n="0669007"><lem>緣生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">因緣</rdg></app>之法念念生滅　喻<note n="0669008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（謂）＋一【甲】</note><app n="0669008"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">謂一</rdg></app>切
<lb n="0669a14"/>事法從緣有。故各無自性。無有停<note n="0669009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">息＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0669009"><lem>息</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">息也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669a15"/><p>實無師子可得<note n="0669010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故名＝名愚法【甲】</note><app n="0669010"><lem>故名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">名愚法</rdg></app>聲聞教　橫計一切境
<lb n="0669a16"/>界實<note n="0669011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝無【甲】</note><app n="0669011"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>自體。但證人空不了法<note n="0669012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0669012"><lem>空</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">空也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669a17"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669a02"/>第二大乘始教<note n="0669013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者謂此師子＝謂即此【甲】</note><app n="0669013"><lem>者謂此師子</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">謂即此</rdg></app>緣生之法各無
<lb n="0669a18"/>自性徹底唯空故名大乘始教　<anchor id="fxT45p0669a03"/>喻<note n="0669014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（謂）＋師【甲】</note><app n="0669014"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">謂師</rdg></app>子無
<lb n="0669a19"/>體。全<note n="0669015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">假＝似【甲】</note><app n="0669015"><lem>假</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">似</rdg></app>真金成工匠緣師子相<note n="0669016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">顯＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0669016"><lem>顯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">顯也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669a20"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669a04"/>第三大乘終教者<note n="0669017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謂此師子雖然＝雖復【甲】</note><app n="0669017"><lem>謂此師子雖然</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">雖復</rdg></app>徹底唯空
<lb n="0669a21"/>不<note n="0669018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">礙＝閡【甲】＊</note><app n="0669018"><lem>礙</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">閡</rdg></app>幻法宛然　雖則真金純一。不<anchor id="fxT45p0669a05"/>礙師
<lb n="0669a22"/>子相存</p>
<lb n="0669a23"/><p>緣生假有二相雙存　真俗二諦歷然可觀。
<lb n="0669a24"/>師子與金兩法齊現</p>
<lb n="0669a25"/><p><note n="0669019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故名＝名為【甲】</note><app n="0669019"><lem>故名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">名為</rdg></app>大乘終教</p>
<lb n="0669a26"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669a06"/>第四大乘頓教者<note n="0669020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔謂〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0669020"><lem>謂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>即此二相互奪兩亡
<lb n="0669a27"/>　以理奪事。事隱理<note n="0669021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">顯＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0669021"><lem>顯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">顯也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669a28"/><p>情偽不存俱無有力空有雙泯名言路絕棲心
<lb n="0669a29"/>無寄　直<note n="0669022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辯＝辨【甲】</note><app n="0669022"><lem>辯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">辨</rdg></app>真性本空。無一法可當情者。
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0669b" n="0669b"/>
<lb n="0669b01"/><note n="0669023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔喻〕－【甲】</note><app n="0669023"><lem>喻</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>金與師子二相俱泯。內外無<note n="0669024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寄＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0669024"><lem>寄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">寄也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669b02"/><p><note n="0669025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0669025"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>名大乘頓教</p>
<lb n="0669b03"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669b01"/>第五一乘圓教者<anchor id="fxT45p0669b02"/>謂即此<note n="0669026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔師子〕－【甲】</note><app n="0669026"><lem>師子</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>情盡體
<lb n="0669b04"/>露之法<note n="0669027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">渾＝混【甲】</note><app n="0669027"><lem>渾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">混</rdg></app>成一塊　<anchor id="fxT45p0669b03"/>喻<note n="0669028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（謂）＋師【甲】</note><app n="0669028"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">謂師</rdg></app>子相盡真金<note n="0669029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">現前＝露現也【甲】</note><app n="0669029"><lem>現
<lb n="0669b05"/>前</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">露現也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669b06"/><p>繁興大用起必<note n="0669030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">全＝金【甲】</note><app n="0669030"><lem>全</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">金</rdg></app>真　<anchor id="fxT45p0669b04"/>喻<note n="0669031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如）＋師【甲】</note><app n="0669031"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">如師</rdg></app>子功用事事
<lb n="0669b07"/>皆<note n="0669032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">金＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0669032"><lem>金</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">金也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669b08"/><p>萬像紛<note n="0669033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">紜＝然【甲】</note><app n="0669033"><lem>紜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">然</rdg></app>參而不雜　雖四<anchor id="fxT45p0669b05"/>像遷移。<note n="0669034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＋（各）【甲】</note><app n="0669034"><lem>各</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">各各</rdg></app>住
<lb n="0669b09"/>自<note n="0669035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">位＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0669035"><lem>位</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">位也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669b10"/><p>一切即一皆同無性　攝末歸本。不<anchor id="fxT45p0669b06"/>礙末也</p>
<lb n="0669b11"/><p>一即一切因果歷然　依本起末。不<anchor id="fxT45p0669b07"/>礙本也</p>
<lb n="0669b12"/><p>力用相收卷舒自在　<note n="0669036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">力＝方【甲】</note><app n="0669036"><lem>力</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">方</rdg></app>顯性起圓融法門
<lb n="0669b13"/>無<anchor id="fxT45p0669b08"/>礙</p>
<lb n="0669b14"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669b09"/>故名一乘圓教</p>
<lb n="0669b15"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669b10"/>第七勒十玄<note n="0669037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">門＝者【甲】</note><app n="0669037"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>一同時具足相應門<note n="0669038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二一…具足門〕七十九字－【甲】</note><note n="0669038" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>〔二一…具足門〕七十九字－【甲】</note>二一
<lb n="0669b16"/>多相容不同門三祕密隱顯俱成門四因陀羅
<lb n="0669b17"/>網境界門五諸藏純雜具德門六諸法相即自
<lb n="0669b18"/>在門七微細相容安立門八十世隔法異成門
<lb n="0669b19"/>九由心&CB04967;轉善成門十託事顯法生解門</p>
<lb n="0669b20"/><p>第一同時具足門謂金與師子同時成立圓滿
<lb n="0669b21"/>具足　<anchor id="fxT45p0669b11"/>喻依法界體起諸事法。隨舉一法具
<lb n="0669b22"/>一切<note n="0669039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＋（雖於一法）【甲】</note><app n="0669039"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">法雖於一法</rdg></app>。別有差別。非<note n="0669040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">造＝迭【甲】</note><app n="0669040"><lem>造</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">迭</rdg></app>玄<note n="0669041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＝矣【甲】</note><app n="0669041"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">矣</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669b23"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669b12"/>故名同時具足相應<note n="0669042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云如海一滴具百川味十一字</note><note n="0669042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云如海一滴具百川味）十一字【甲】</note><app n="0669042"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云如海一滴具百川味</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669b24"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669b13"/>第二一多相容不同門<note n="0669043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【甲】</note><app n="0669043"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>謂金與師子相容
<lb n="0669b25"/>成立一多無<anchor id="fxT45p0669b14"/>礙於中理事各各不同<note n="0669044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＋（一或）【甲】</note><app n="0669044"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">或一或</rdg></app>多各
<lb n="0669b26"/>住自位　如稱理之行一一各容一切諸法。
<lb n="0669b27"/>亦一一各具一切諸行。雖相容本不動<anchor id="fxT45p0669b15"/>也</p>
<lb n="0669b28"/><p>故名一多相容不同<note n="0669045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云若一室之千燈光光即涉也十四字</note><note n="0669045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云若一室之千燈光光即涉也）十四字【甲】</note><app n="0669045"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云若一室之千燈光光即涉也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669b29"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669b16"/>第三祕密隱顯俱成門<anchor id="fxT45p0669b17"/>者謂若看師子唯見
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0669c" n="0669c"/>
<lb n="0669c01"/>師子無金則師子顯金隱　<anchor id="fxT45p0669c01"/>喻<note n="0669046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如）＋事【甲】</note><app n="0669046"><lem>事</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">如事</rdg></app>能隱<note n="0669047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">理＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0669047"><lem>理</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">理也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669c02"/><p>若看金<note n="0669048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＋（見）【甲】</note><app n="0669048"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">唯見</rdg></app>金無師子則金顯師子隱　<anchor id="fxT45p0669c02"/>喻<note n="0669049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如）＋理【甲】</note><app n="0669049"><lem>理</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">如理</rdg></app>
<lb n="0669c03"/>能隱事也</p>
<lb n="0669c04"/><p>若兩處看俱<note n="0669050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">顯＝隱【甲】</note><app n="0669050"><lem>顯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">隱</rdg></app>俱顯隱則祕密顯則顯著<note n="0669051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故名＝名為【甲】＊</note><app n="0669051"><lem>故
<lb n="0669c05"/>名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">名為</rdg></app>祕密隱顯俱成<note n="0669052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云若片月澄空晦明相並十二字</note><note n="0669052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云若片月澄空晦明相並）十二字【甲】</note><app n="0669052"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云若片月澄空晦明相並</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669c06"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669c03"/>第四因陀羅網境界門<note n="0669053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者謂〕－【甲】</note><app n="0669053"><lem>者謂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>師子眼耳支節
<lb n="0669c07"/>一一毛處各有金師子　<note n="0669054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">小＝一【甲】</note><app n="0669054"><lem>小</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app>法中含<note n="0669055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大法＝多法小法中有大法【甲】</note><app n="0669055"><lem>大法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">多法小法中有大法</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669c08"/><p>一一毛處師子同時頓入一莖毛中各各顯露
<lb n="0669c09"/>皆有無邊師子　一事中含多事。一多<note n="0669056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頓現＝顯現也【甲】</note><app n="0669056"><lem>頓現</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">顯現也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669c10"/><p>一一毛頭帶此無邊師子還入一莖毛中如是
<lb n="0669c11"/>重重無盡　<note n="0669057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一橫多）＋多【甲】</note><app n="0669057"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一橫多多</rdg></app>入一無<note n="0669058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">礙＝閡也【甲】</note><app n="0669058"><lem>礙</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">閡也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669c12"/><p>若帝網<note n="0669059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之天珠故＝天珠【甲】</note><app n="0669059"><lem>之天珠故</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">天珠</rdg></app>名因陀羅網境界<note n="0669060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云若兩鏡互照交耀相寫迭出無盡十六字</note><note n="0669060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云若兩鏡互照交耀相寫迭出無盡）十六字【甲】</note><app n="0669060"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云若兩鏡互照交耀相寫迭出無盡</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669c13"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669c04"/>第五諸藏純雜具德門<anchor id="fxT45p0669c05"/>者謂<note n="0669061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝即此師子【甲】</note><app n="0669061"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">即此師子</rdg></app>以眼收師
<lb n="0669c14"/>子盡則一切純是眼　如以布施一行收盡一
<lb n="0669c15"/>切行總名布施故。號曰純也</p>
<lb n="0669c16"/><p>若耳收師子盡則一切純是耳若諸根同時
<lb n="0669c17"/><note n="0669062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔相〕－【甲】</note><app n="0669062"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>收悉皆具足一一皆<note n="0669063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">純＝雜亦【甲】</note><app n="0669063"><lem>純</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">雜亦</rdg></app>一一皆<note n="0669064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雜＝純【甲】</note><app n="0669064"><lem>雜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">純</rdg></app>是圓
<lb n="0669c18"/>滿藏　萬行同時。更互莊嚴。純雜無<anchor id="fxT45p0669c06"/>礙</p>
<lb n="0669c19"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669c07"/>故名諸藏純雜具德<note n="0669065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云譬如北辰所居眾星拱之十三字</note><note n="0669065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云譬如北辰所居眾星拱之）十三字【甲】</note><app n="0669065"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云譬如北辰所居眾星拱之</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0669c20"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0669c08"/>第六諸法相即自在門<anchor id="fxT45p0669c09"/>者謂即師子諸根一
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0670a" n="0670a"/>
<lb n="0670a01"/>一毛頭皆各<note n="0670001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以金＝全【甲】</note><app n="0670001"><lem>以金</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">全</rdg></app>收師子盡　<anchor id="fxT45p0670a01"/>喻<note n="0670002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（謂）＋法【甲】</note><app n="0670002"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">謂法</rdg></app>界緣
<lb n="0670a02"/>起一切諸法皆互相即相遍也</p>
<lb n="0670a03"/><p>一一皆徹師子眼眼即耳耳即鼻<note n="0670003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無礙無障＝等無障無閡【甲】</note><app n="0670003"><lem>無礙無障</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">等無障無閡</rdg></app>
<lb n="0670a04"/>　<anchor id="fxT45p0670a02"/>喻布施即<note n="0670004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">九＝相【甲】</note><app n="0670004"><lem>九</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">相</rdg></app>度。多行即一行也</p>
<lb n="0670a05"/><p>故名諸法相即自在<note n="0670005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云如金與金色二不相離十二字</note><note n="0670005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云如金與金色二不相離）十二字【甲】</note><app n="0670005"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云如金與金色二不相離</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0670a06"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0670a03"/>第七微細相容安立門<anchor id="fxT45p0670a04"/>者謂金與師子<note n="0670006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或隱或顯＝或顯或隱【甲】</note><app n="0670006"><lem>或
<lb n="0670a07"/>隱或顯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">或顯或隱</rdg></app>或一或多定散同時　經云。汝應觀
<lb n="0670a08"/>我諸毛孔。我今示汝。佛境界俱時歷<note n="0670007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">然＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0670007"><lem>然</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">然也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0670a09"/><p>即此即彼有力無力主伴交<note n="0670008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輝＝耀【甲】</note><app n="0670008"><lem>輝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">耀</rdg></app>理事齊現
<lb n="0670a10"/>　所現萬法海印炳然</p>
<lb n="0670a11"/><p>悉皆相容不<anchor id="fxT45p0670a05"/>礙安立微細成<note n="0670009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辦＝雜【甲】</note><app n="0670009"><lem>辦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">雜</rdg></app>　以理成事。
<lb n="0670a12"/>事法不定互相容攝安立同時</p>
<lb n="0670a13"/><p>故名微細相容安立<note n="0670010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云如琉璃壺盛多芥子十一字</note><note n="0670010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云如琉璃壺盛多芥子）十一字【甲】</note><app n="0670010"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云如琉璃壺盛多芥子</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0670a14"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0670a06"/>第八十世隔法異成門者謂<note n="0670011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670011"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>師子是有為
<lb n="0670a15"/>之法念念生滅　<anchor id="fxT45p0670a07"/>喻<note n="0670012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（謂）＋真【甲】</note><app n="0670012"><lem>真</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">謂真</rdg></app>理隨緣成諸事法各
<lb n="0670a16"/>各<note n="0670013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不實＝遷變不停【甲】</note><app n="0670013"><lem>不實</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">遷變不停</rdg></app>也</p>
<lb n="0670a17"/><p>剎那之間分為三際謂<note n="0670014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670014"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>過去未來現在<note n="0670015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三際〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670015"><lem>三
<lb n="0670a18"/>際</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>　總相之中分限不同</p>
<lb n="0670a19"/><p>總有三三之位以立九世　一即多多不<note n="0670016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">壞＋（一）【甲】</note><app n="0670016"><lem>壞</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">壞一</rdg></app>
<lb n="0670a20"/>則束為一段法門　一法門中無<note n="0670017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">量＝盡【甲】</note><app n="0670017"><lem>量</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">盡</rdg></app>門種種
<lb n="0670a21"/>脩短各<note n="0670018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔各〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670018"><lem>各</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不同</p>
<lb n="0670a22"/><p>雖則九世<note n="0670019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有隔不同＝各各有隔【甲】</note><app n="0670019"><lem>有隔不同</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">各各有隔</rdg></app>相由成立融通無<anchor id="fxT45p0670a08"/>礙同
<lb n="0670a23"/>為一念　攝末歸本</p>
<lb n="0670a24"/><p>故號十世隔法異成<note n="0670020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云若一夕夢翱翔百年十一字</note><note n="0670020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云若一夕夢翱翔百年）十一字【甲】</note><app n="0670020"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云若一夕夢翱翔百年</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0670a25"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0670a09"/>第九由心迴轉善成門<anchor id="fxT45p0670a10"/>者謂金與師子或顯
<lb n="0670a26"/>或隱或一或多各無自性由心迴轉　法無定
<lb n="0670a27"/>法。隨心轉變</p>
<lb n="0670a28"/><p>說理說事有成<note n="0670021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（有）＋立【甲】</note><app n="0670021"><lem>立</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">有立</rdg></app>　法本具足。隨機隱顯</p>
<lb n="0670a29"/><p>故名由心迴轉善成<note n="0670022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云如一尺之鏡見千里之象十三字</note><note n="0670022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云如一尺之鏡見千里之象）十三字【甲】</note><app n="0670022"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云如一尺之鏡見千里之象</rdg></app></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0670b" n="0670b"/>
<lb n="0670b01"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0670b01"/>第十託事顯法生解門<anchor id="fxT45p0670b02"/>者謂說師子用<note n="0670023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋表【甲】</note><app n="0670023"><lem>表</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">以表</rdg></app>
<lb n="0670b02"/>無明論此金體具彰真性　<note n="0670024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00418;＝視【甲】</note><app n="0670024"><lem>&CB00418;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">視</rdg></app>萬法相用顯
<lb n="0670b03"/>真理</p>
<lb n="0670b04"/><p>若理事合論況阿賴耶識令生正解　即染而
<lb n="0670b05"/>淨。動<note n="0670025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨＝靜【甲】</note><app n="0670025"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">靜</rdg></app>俱泯方為正解</p>
<lb n="0670b06"/><p>故名託事顯法生解<note n="0670026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有清涼云立像&CB00594;辟觸目皆道也十二字</note><note n="0670026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（清涼云立像&CB00594;辟觸目皆道也）十二字【甲】</note><app n="0670026"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">門清涼云立像&CB00594;辟觸目皆道也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0670b07"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0670b03"/>第八括六相者　<anchor id="fxT45p0670b04"/>謂師子是總相五根差別
<lb n="0670b08"/><note n="0670027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝為【甲】</note><app n="0670027"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>別相<note n="0670028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">共＋（成）【甲】</note><app n="0670028"><lem>共</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">共成</rdg></app>一緣起是同相眼耳各不相<note n="0670029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">到是為＝知是【甲】</note><app n="0670029"><lem>到
<lb n="0670b09"/>是為</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">知是</rdg></app>異相諸根<note n="0670030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＝共【甲】</note><app n="0670030"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">共</rdg></app>會是成相諸緣各住自位
<lb n="0670b10"/>是壞相　顯法界中無孤單法。隨舉一<note n="0670031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相＝法【甲】</note><app n="0670031"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>。具
<lb n="0670b11"/>此六相緣起。<note n="0670032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">集＝奪無【甲】</note><app n="0670032"><lem>集</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">奪無</rdg></app>成各無自性。一一相中含無
<lb n="0670b12"/>盡相。一一法中具無盡<note n="0670033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0670033"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">法也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0670b13"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0670b05"/>第九成菩提者此云<note n="0670034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道也覺也＝覺也道也【甲】</note><app n="0670034"><lem>道也覺也</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">覺也道也</rdg></app>　略<note n="0670035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說＝就【甲】</note><app n="0670035"><lem>說</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">就</rdg></app>唐
<lb n="0670b14"/>言。有此二義</p>
<lb n="0670b15"/><p>眼見師子之時<note n="0670036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（即）＋一【甲】</note><app n="0670036"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">即一</rdg></app>切有為<note n="0670037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝之【甲】</note><app n="0670037"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>法更不待壞本
<lb n="0670b16"/>來寂滅　<anchor id="fxT45p0670b06"/>喻<note n="0670038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如）＋師【甲】</note><app n="0670038"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">如師</rdg></app>子相不實。當體是金不<note n="0670039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">可＝待【甲】</note><app n="0670039"><lem>可</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">待</rdg></app>
<lb n="0670b17"/>壞也</p>
<lb n="0670b18"/><p>離諸取捨即於此路流入薩婆若海故名為道
<lb n="0670b19"/>也　諸法無生。畢竟空寂。包含無外。不拒眾
<lb n="0670b20"/>流。大道無邊。悟則斯在。是故<note n="0670040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00418;＝規【甲】</note><app n="0670040"><lem>&CB00418;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">規</rdg></app>此師<note n="0670041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="0670041"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">子之</rdg></app>相。
<lb n="0670b21"/>便入一切智海。更無異路。薩婆若者此云無
<lb n="0670b22"/><note n="0670042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="0670042"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">生之</rdg></app>智也</p>
<lb n="0670b23"/><p>即了無始已來所有顛倒元無<note n="0670043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">實有名之＝有實故名【甲】</note><app n="0670043"><lem>實有名之</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">有實故名</rdg></app>為
<lb n="0670b24"/>覺　妄起諸顛倒。都無有實體。正覺若現前。
<lb n="0670b25"/>如空皆寂滅。即外無纖塵。內無識念<anchor id="fxT45p0670b07"/>也</p>
<lb n="0670b26"/><p>畢竟具一切種智名成菩提　一悟永悟。一
<lb n="0670b27"/>成永<note n="0670044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成＋（無一法而不了無一行而不圓無一智而不具無一理而不證）【甲】</note><app n="0670044"><lem>成</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">成無一法而不了無一行而不圓無一智而不具無一理而不證</rdg></app>。大智現前更無餘<note n="0670045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">物＝法【甲】</note><app n="0670045"><lem>物</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>即成菩提也</p>
<lb n="0670b28"/><p><anchor id="fxT45p0670b08"/>第十入涅槃者謂見師子與金二相俱盡
<lb n="0670b29"/>　喻也</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T45.1881.0670c" n="0670c"/>
<lb n="0670c01"/><p>煩惱不生好醜現前　身心相盡煩惱不生。
<lb n="0670c02"/>即大涅槃究竟玄寂</p>
<lb n="0670c03"/><p>心安如海　經云。若<note n="0670046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔能〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670046"><lem>能</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>安心如海。<note n="0670047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（於）＋中【甲】</note><app n="0670047"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">於中</rdg></app>好醜
<lb n="0670c04"/>皆空無所<note n="0670048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＋（也）【甲】</note><app n="0670048"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">住也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0670c05"/><p>妄想都盡無諸逼迫出纏離障永離苦源名
<lb n="0670c06"/><note n="0670049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670049"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>入涅槃也　<note n="0670050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妄＋（想都）【甲】</note><app n="0670050"><lem>妄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">妄想都</rdg></app>盡全<note n="0670051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">真＋（理）【甲】</note><app n="0670051"><lem>真</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">真理</rdg></app>。無諸逼迫。任逍
<lb n="0670c07"/>遙出纏。魔惱不相侵<note n="0670052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔奪〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670052"><lem>奪</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。離障法門無<note n="0670053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670053"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>滯
<lb n="0670c08"/><anchor id="fxT45p0670c01"/>礙湛然寂靜<note n="0670054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔常〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670054"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>安樂。利益群生出苦源。我
<lb n="0670c09"/>今稽首獲無餘。一切有情同解脫。肇公云。功
<lb n="0670c10"/>流萬世<note n="0670055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔而〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670055"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>常存。道通百劫而彌固。成山假就
<lb n="0670c11"/>於始簀修途託至於<note n="0670056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">初＝劫【甲】</note><app n="0670056"><lem>初</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">劫</rdg></app>步果以功業不可杇
<lb n="0670c12"/><note n="0670057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故〕－【甲】</note><app n="0670057"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>也。然三乘之教有次第故。圓頓之<note n="0670058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">理＝詮【甲】</note><app n="0670058"><lem>理</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">詮</rdg></app>渾
<lb n="0670c13"/>融無<anchor id="fxT45p0670c02"/>礙。一法之上了一切法。一行之中具一
<lb n="0670c14"/>切行。因該果海。果徹因源。果是即因之果。因
<lb n="0670c15"/>是即果之因。平等無二相也。<note n="0670059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（故）＋經【甲】</note><app n="0670059"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">故經</rdg></app>云。平等真
<lb n="0670c16"/>法<note n="0670060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">界＝性【甲】</note><app n="0670060"><lem>界</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">性</rdg></app>無佛無眾生<note n="0670061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矣＝故也又經云能隨染淨緣道分十法界【甲】</note><app n="0670061"><lem>矣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">故也又經云能隨染淨緣道分十法界</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0670c17"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0670062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大方廣佛華嚴經＝註【甲】</note><app n="0670062"><lem>大方廣佛華嚴經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">註</rdg></app>金師子章一<note n="0670063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">卷＋（終）【甲】</note><app n="0670063"><lem>卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">卷終</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
